ompany to the cloud. Maintaining the usage of cloud services and implementing cost-saving strategies.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Here\n					</a>\n		<h3>Java full stack developer-2</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Java, Node/Angular/React JS, Git, GitHub and Sourcetree, Databases and Web Storage, Web Architecture, HTTP and REST. by others and analysing results.                                                                 </p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Here\n					</a>\n		<h3>Python full stack-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Python, Node/Angular/React JS, Basic design ability, Server, Version control system (VCS), Working with API (REST &amp; SOAP).</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Here\n					</a>\n		<h3>Cyber security engineer-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Great Problem-Solving Skills, In-depth technical knowledge of computer sciences, Knowledge of Security Across Various Platforms, Attention to Detail, Communication Skills, Fundamental Computer Forensics Skills, Ethical hacking       </p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Here\n					</a>\n		<h3>Mule soft-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Integration Lead who can design and build the integrations flows, RAML, Swagger based RESTful APIs and SOAP APIs ensuring Mulesoft best practices. Lead should have experience on building (MuleSoft Experience APIs, Process APIs and System APIs) and Batch Process.   </p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Here\n					</a>\n		<h3>Project Manager-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Activity and resource planning, Organizing and motivating a project team, Controlling time management, Cost estimating and developing the budget, Ensuring customer satisfaction, Analyzing and managing project risk, Monitoring progress, Managing reports and necessary documentation, controlling, and closing projects.  </p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Here\n					</a>\n		