ineer</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Identifying and selecting the automation test cases Applying various designs and documenting the automation test strategy Creating an automation test plan and getting approval Configuring Selenium Test Environment (STE) in order to set it up results.                                                                 </p>		\n		<h3>Application Platform Engineer</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Assist to install and configure all Oracle Fusion Middleware and manage efficient configuration of all Oracle RAC databases. Supervise all application packing processes and maintain optimal quality for all applications.     </p>		\n		<h3>Infrastructure Engineer</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Establish Network Infrastructure Whether they’re building a whole IT network or setting up a PC and access permissions for a new hire, IT infrastructure engineers provide the technological foundation for much of their organization’s day-to-day operations.           </p>		\n		<h3>AZure Devops engineer</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Designing DevOps Strategy Implementing DevOps Development Processes Implementing Continuous Integration, Continuous Delivery Implementing Dependency Management, Application Infrastructure Implementing Continuous Feedback           </p>		\n		<h3>Cloud engineer</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Designing and deploying apps on a cloud. Identifying and using the appropriate cloud services to support apps on the cloud. Migrating on-premise apps of the company to the cloud. Maintaining the usage of cloud services and implementing cost-saving strategies.</p>		\n		<h3>Java full stack developer-2</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Java, Node/Angular/React JS, Git, GitHub and Sourcetree, Databases and Web Storage, Web Architecture, HTTP and REST. by others and analysing results.                                                                 </p>		\n		<h3>Python full stack-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Python, Node/Angular/React JS, Basic design ability, Server, Version control system (VCS), Working with API (REST &amp; SOAP).</p>		\n		<h3>Cyber security engineer-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Great Problem-Solving Skills, In-depth technical knowledge of computer sciences, Knowledge of Security Across Various Platforms, Attention to Detail, Communication Skills, Fundamental Computer Forensics Skills, Ethical hacking       </p>		\n		<h3>Mule soft-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Integration Lead who can design and build the integrations flows, RAML, Swagger based RESTful APIs and SOAP APIs ensuring Mulesoft best practices. Lead should have experience on building (MuleSoft Experience APIs, Process APIs and System APIs) and Batch Process.   </p>		\n		<h3>Project Manager-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Activity and resource planning, Organizing and motivating a project team, Controlling time management, Cost estimating and developing the budget, Ensuring customer satisfaction, Analyzing and managing project risk, Monitoring progress, Managing reports and necessary documentation, controlling, and closing projects.  </p>		\n		<h3>Site reliability Engineer-1</h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Continuous Integration and Delivery (CI/CD) across SDLC phases, Monitoring, Alerts, Incident Response, Infrastructure Component Provisioning, Patching.</p>', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-04-30 07:00:00', '2022-04-30 07:00:00', '', 10, 'https://venkat.asntechnoservice.com/?p=159', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
